#. Tag: title
#: synchronizer.docbook:8 synchronizer.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Synchronizer</title>"
msgstr "<title>Sinhronizator</title>"

#. Tag: primary
#: synchronizer.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "<primary>Synchronizer</primary>"
msgstr "<primary>Sinhronizator</primary>"

#. Tag: title
#: synchronizer.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function compares two folders with all subfolders and shows the "
"differences between them. After selecting some options and the "
"<guilabel>Compare</guilabel> function you can synchronize the files and "
"folders. One panel could be an &FTP; server. Do not forget the "
"<guilabel>Compare by content</guilabel> option if the file size stays equal. "
"Choose <menuchoice> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Synchronize "
"Folders</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; "
"<keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo> to start this feature. The <link linkend="
"\"konfig-color\">colors</link> are configurable. The synchronizer has its "
"own <link linkend=\"synchronizer_keybindings\">keybindings</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija primerja dve mapi z vsemi podmapami in prikaže razlike med "
"njima. Ko izberete nekaj možnosti in funkcijo <guilabel>Primerjaj</"
"guilabel>, lahko sinhronizirate datoteke in mape. Ena plošča je lahko &FTP; "
"strežnik. Ne pozabite na možnost <guilabel>Primerjaj po vsebini</guilabel>, "
"če velikost datoteke ostane enaka. Izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sinhroniziraj mape</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ali "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo> za zagon te "
"funkcije. <link linkend=\"konfig-color\">Barve</link> so nastavljive. "
"Sinhronizator ima lastne <link linkend=\"synchronizer_keybindings\">veze "
"tipk</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For local files: The synchronizer changes the date information to the "
"original dates."
msgstr ""
"Za lokalne datoteke: Sinhronizator spremeni podatke o datumu na izvirne "
"datume."

#. Tag: phrase
#: synchronizer.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Synchronizer</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Sinhronizator</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: synchronizer.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Procedure:"
msgstr "Postopek:"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the <guilabel>Left folder</guilabel> and the <guilabel>Right folder</"
"guilabel> that you want to compare."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite <guilabel>levo mapo</guilabel> in <guilabel>desno mapo</guilabel>, "
"ki ju želite primerjati."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the optional <guilabel>File Filter</guilabel>, <guilabel>General "
"Filters</guilabel> and <guilabel>Advanced filters</guilabel>. The "
"<guilabel>General Filters</guilabel> includes a <guilabel>Do not search in</"
"guilabel> option which lets you exclude folders from comparison."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte izbirni <guilabel>Filter datotek</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Splošne filtre</guilabel> in <guilabel>Napredne filtre</guilabel>. "
"<guilabel>Splošni filtri</guilabel> vključujejo možnost <guilabel>Ne išči v</"
"guilabel>, ki vam omogoča izključitev map iz primerjave."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the <link linkend=\"synccomp_checkb_options\">Checkbox options</link>: "
"<guilabel>Recurse subfolders</guilabel>, <guilabel>Follow symlinks</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Compare by content</guilabel>, <guilabel>Ignore Date</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Asymmetric</guilabel> and <guilabel>Ignore Case</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite <link linkend=\"synccomp_checkb_options\">možnosti potrditvenega "
"polja</link>: <guilabel>Ponovne podmape</guilabel>, <guilabel>Sledi "
"simbolnim povezavam</guilabel>, <guilabel>Primerjaj po vsebini</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel >Prezri datum</guilabel>, <guilabel>Asimetrično</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Prezri velike in male črke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <guibutton>Compare</guibutton> button to compare the folders."
msgstr "Kliknite na gumb <guibutton>Primerjaj</guibutton>, da primerjate mape."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By using <link linkend=\"synccomp_show_options\">Show options</link>, you "
"can include/exclude particular file types. The files that are not on the "
"list will be untouched by synchronization."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo <link linkend=\"synccomp_show_options\">Možnosti prikaza</link> "
"lahko vključite/izključite določene vrste datotek. Datoteke, ki niso na "
"seznamu, bodo s sinhronizacijo nedotaknjene."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If needed, you can change the <guilabel>Task</guilabel> operations "
"determined by the Comparator with the <link linkend=\"synccomp_right-click"
"\">right click menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"Po potrebi lahko spremenite operacije <guilabel>Opravila</guilabel>, ki jih "
"določi primerjalnik z <link linkend=\"synccomp_right-click\">menijem z "
"desnim klikom</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you agree with the <guibutton>Compare</guibutton> results, click on the "
"<guibutton>Synchronize</guibutton> button to show the synchronize dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko se strinjate z rezultati <guibutton>Primerjaj</guibutton>, kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Sinhroniziraj</guibutton>, da prikažete pogovorno okno za "
"sinhronizacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After selecting the options of the <link linkend=\"synchronizer"
"\">Synchronizer</link>, click on the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> button to "
"start the synchronization process."
msgstr ""
"Po izbiri možnosti <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Sinhronizatorja</link> "
"kliknite na gumb <guibutton>Začni</guibutton>, da začnete postopek "
"sinhronizacije."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A detailed explanation of all the functions and buttons is described in the "
"following text."
msgstr ""
"Podrobna razlaga vseh funkcij in gumbov je opisana v naslednjem besedilu."

#. Tag: title
#: synchronizer.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Comparator"
msgstr "Primerjalnik"

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Panel elements"
msgstr "Elementi plošče"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Left Directory</guilabel>: The left side base folder."
msgstr "<guilabel>Levi imenik</guilabel>: Osnovna mapa na levi strani."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Right Directory</guilabel>: The right side base folder."
msgstr "<guilabel>Desni imenik</guilabel>: desna osnovna mapa."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>File Filter</guilabel>: Filters the filenames at synchronizing. "
"&eg; <literal role=\"extension\">*.png</literal> selects only files the "
"names of which end with <literal role=\"extension\">.png</literal>. Folders "
"are listed if the folder name ends with <literal role=\"extension\">.png</"
"literal> or if the folder contains files which end with <literal role="
"\"extension\">.png</literal>. Multiple include/exclude example: <literal "
"role=\"extension\">'*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp'</literal> includes <literal role="
"\"extension\">*.cpp *.h</literal> and exclude <literal role=\"extension\">*."
"moc.cpp</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Filter datotek</guilabel>: Filtrira imena datotek pri "
"sinhronizaciji. &eg; <literal role=\"extension\">*.png</literal> izbere samo "
"datoteke, katerih imena se končajo z <literal role=\"extension\">.png</"
"literal>. Mape so navedene, če se ime mape konča z <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.png</literal> ali če mapa vsebuje datoteke, ki se končajo z <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.png</literal>. Primer več vključitev/izključitev: "
"<literal role=\"extension\">'*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp'</literal> vključuje "
"<literal role=\"extension\">*.cpp *.h</literal> in izključuje <literal role="
"\"extension\">*.moc.cpp</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General filters</guilabel>: Search for, containing text"
msgstr "<guilabel>Splošni filtri</guilabel>: Iskanje, ki vsebuje besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Advanced filters</guilabel>: Size, date, ownership"
msgstr "<guilabel>Napredni filtri</guilabel>: velikost, datum, lastništvo"

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filename filtering criteria"
msgstr "Kriteriji filtriranja imena datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make use of wild cards. Multiple patterns are separated by space "
"(means logical OR) and patterns are excluded from the search using the pipe "
"symbol. If the pattern is ended with a slash (*pattern*/), it means that "
"pattern relates to recursive search of folders."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko nadomestne znake. Več vzorcev je ločenih s presledkom "
"(pomeni logični ALI), vzorci pa so izključeni iz iskanja z uporabo črte. Če "
"se vzorec konča s poševnico (*vzorec*/), to pomeni, da se vzorec nanaša na "
"rekurzivno iskanje map."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"pattern - means to search those files/folders whose name is a pattern, "
"recursive search goes through all subfolders independently of the value of "
"the pattern."
msgstr ""
"vzorec - pomeni iskanje tistih datotek/map, katerih ime je vzorec, "
"rekurzivno iskanje gre skozi vse podmape neodvisno od vrednosti vzorca."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"pattern/ - means to search all files/folders, but recursive search goes "
"through/excludes the folders whose name is a pattern."
msgstr ""
"vzorec/ - pomeni iskanje po vseh datotekah/mapah, vendar rekurzivno iskanje "
"poteka skozi/izključuje mape, katerih ime je vzorec."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use quotation marks for names that contain spaces. Filter "
"<quote>Program Files</quote> searches out those files/folders the name of "
"which is <filename>Program Files</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Za imena, ki vsebujejo presledke, lahko uporabite narekovaje. Filter "
"<quote>Programske datoteke</quote> išče tiste datoteke/mape, katerih ime je "
"<filename>Programske datoteke</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: literal
#: synchronizer.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>*.o</literal>"
msgstr "<literal>*.o</literal>"

#. Tag: literal
#: synchronizer.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "*.h *.c??"
msgstr "*.h *.c??"

#. Tag: literal
#: synchronizer.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp"
msgstr "*.cpp *.h | *.moc.cpp"

#. Tag: literal
#: synchronizer.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "* | CVS/ .svn/"
msgstr "* | CVS/ .svn/"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note: the search term 'text' is equivalent to '*text*'."
msgstr "Opomba: iskalni izraz 'besedilo' je enakovreden '*besedilo*'."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Checkbox options"
msgstr "Možnosti potrditvenega polja"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Recurse subfolders</guilabel>: The Synchronizer walks through "
"subfolders when comparing."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ponovne podmape</guilabel>: Sinhronizator se med primerjavo "
"sprehaja skozi podmape."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Follow symlinks</guilabel>: The Synchronizer follows the symbolic "
"links to folders (not the files!)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Sledi simbolnim povezavam</guilabel>: Sinhronizator sledi "
"simbolnim povezavam do map (ne datotek!)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Compare by content</guilabel>: The files the sizes of which are "
"equal will be compared by content as well."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Primerjaj po vsebini</guilabel>: Datoteke, katerih velikosti so "
"enake, bodo primerjane tudi po vsebini."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ignore Date</guilabel>: Ignores the date information (useful for "
"&FTP;, smb, archive, ... ) the date information is relevant *only* in the "
"local file system."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prezri datum</guilabel>: Prezri informacijo o datumu (uporabno za "
"&FTP;, smb, arhiv, ...) informacija o datumu je pomembna *samo* v lokalnem "
"datotečnem sistemu."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Asymmetric</guilabel>: The <guilabel>Left Directory</guilabel> is "
"the target folder, the <guilabel>Right Directory</guilabel> is the source "
"folder. This function synchronizes the content of the left folder to the "
"right folder. <itemizedlist> <listitem> <para>The files that exist only on "
"the left side will be deleted.</para> </listitem> <listitem> <para>The files "
"that exist only on the right side will be copied to left.</para> </listitem> "
"<listitem> <para>The files considered to be equal will be untouched.</para> "
"</listitem> <listitem> <para>Those files considered to be different will be "
"copied to left. Use this feature with care!</para> <itemizedlist> <listitem> "
"<para>Note that there is a measure to avoid data losses: if dates are taken "
"into account (because <guilabel>Ignore Date</guilabel> is disabled), then "
"the default action is <emphasis>not to overwrite a file by an old version of "
"it</emphasis>. The user is still able to overwrite (by right-clicking and "
"selecting <guilabel>Copy from right to left</guilabel>).</para> </listitem> "
"</itemizedlist> </listitem> </itemizedlist>This function is useful if the "
"date information is unusable, or to synchronize the left folder to the "
"content of a file server (like a download). Alternatively, it is useful to "
"make a backup from the right folder to the left folder. NOTE: Do NOT use "
"this option to synchronize a desktop and a notebook (&eg; files that exist "
"only on the left side will be deleted!)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Asimetrično</guilabel>: <guilabel>Levi imenik</guilabel> je ciljna "
"mapa, <guilabel>Desni imenik</guilabel> je izvorna mapa. Ta funkcija "
"sinhronizira vsebino leve mape z desno mapo. <itemizedlist> <listitem> "
"<para>Datoteke, ki obstajajo samo na levi strani, bodo izbrisane.</para> </"
"listitem> <listitem> <para>Datoteke, ki obstajajo samo na desni strani, bodo "
"kopirane na levo. .</para> </listitem> <listitem> <para>Datoteke, ki se "
"štejejo za enake, bodo nedotaknjene.</para> </listitem> <listitem> "
"<para>Datoteke, ki se štejejo za različne, bodo kopirane na levo . To "
"funkcijo uporabljajte previdno!</para> <itemizedlist> <listitem> "
"<para>Upoštevajte, da obstaja ukrep za preprečevanje izgube podatkov: če so "
"upoštevani datumi (ker je <guilabel>Prezri datum</guilabel> onemogočen) , "
"potem je privzeto dejanje <emphasis>ne prepisati datoteke z njeno staro "
"različico</emphasis>. Uporabnik lahko še vedno prepisuje (z desnim klikom in "
"izbiro <guilabel>Kopiraj od desne proti levi</guilabel>).</para> </listitem> "
"</itemizedlist> </listitem> </itemizedlist>Ta funkcija je uporabna, če "
"informacije o datumu niso uporabne ali za sinhronizacijo leve mape z vsebino "
"datotečnega strežnika (kot prenos). Druga možnost je, da naredite varnostno "
"kopijo iz desne mape v levo mapo. OPOMBA: NE uporabljajte te možnosti za "
"sinhronizacijo namizja in prenosnika (&eg;  datoteke, ki obstajajo le na "
"levi strani, bodo izbrisane!)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Scroll Results</guilabel>: This is for slow &FTP; servers, ... "
"When the Synchronizer has finished comparing a file, it puts the file into "
"the end of the list at once and scrolls the window, if necessary. It is "
"important, if you want to know what the Synchronizer is doing. If the &FTP; "
"server is slow, the comparison of a folder may take a lot of time. By "
"turning this option on, you can see that the comparator is <quote>alive</"
"quote>, but slow. For fast file systems, it can reduce the speed of "
"comparing slightly."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Premikanje rezultatov</guilabel>: To je za počasen &FTP; "
"strežniki, ... Ko sinhronizator konča s primerjavo datoteke, jo takoj "
"postavi na konec seznama in po potrebi pomakne okno. Pomembno je, če želite "
"vedeti, kaj počne sinhronizator. Če &FTP; strežnik je počasen, lahko "
"primerjava mape traja veliko časa. Če vklopite to možnost, lahko vidite, da "
"je primerjalnik <quote>živ</quote>, vendar počasen. Za hitre datotečne "
"sisteme lahko nekoliko zmanjša hitrost primerjave."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ignore Case</guilabel>: Case insensitive filename compare, this is "
"useful when synchronizing &Windows; filesystems."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prezri velike in male črke</guilabel>: Primerjava imen datotek "
"brez upoštevanja velikih in malih črk, to je uporabno pri sinhronizaciji "
"&Windows; datotečni sistemi."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ignore hidden files</guilabel>: Ignores files that start with a "
"dot."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prezri skrite datoteke</guilabel>: Prezre datoteke, ki se začnejo "
"s piko."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When everything mentioned above is done, click on the <guibutton>Compare</"
"guibutton> button to compare the folders, the results are displayed in the "
"<guilabel>File List</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je vse zgoraj omenjeno opravljeno, kliknite gumb <guibutton>Primerjaj</"
"guibutton>, da primerjate mape, rezultati so prikazani na <guilabel>Seznamu "
"datotek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "File List"
msgstr "Seznam datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>File List</guilabel> has the following columns: <quote>Left "
"name | Left size | Left time | Task | Right time | Right size | Right name</"
"quote>. Here you can check the compare results and modify the "
"synchronization actions if desired. The text color defines the default copy "
"direction determined by the comparator. <itemizedlist> <listitem> "
"<para>Green: Copy from left to right.</para> </listitem> <listitem> "
"<para>Blue: Copy from right to left or delete on the right side in "
"asymmetric mode.</para> </listitem> <listitem> <para>Red: Files which are "
"different by the given criteria (no copy direction).</para> </listitem> "
"<listitem> <para>Black: Files which are identical (no copy direction).</"
"para> </listitem> </itemizedlist> A double click on a file calls the "
"&krusader;s <guilabel>Compare by content</guilabel> function. The Tasks (&lt;"
"=&gt;) column defines the default copy direction, which can be modified by "
"the user if needed. The results window supports dragging items to other "
"windows ( drag [left], &Shift;+drag [right] ) and copy left/right selected "
"items to clipboard (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Seznam datotek</guilabel> ima naslednje stolpce: <quote>Levo ime | "
"Leva velikost | Preostali čas | Naloga | Pravi čas | Prava velikost | Pravo "
"ime</quote>. Tukaj lahko preverite rezultate primerjave in po želji "
"spremenite dejanja sinhronizacije. Barva besedila določa privzeto smer "
"kopiranja, ki jo določi primerjalnik. <itemizedlist> <listitem> "
"<para>Zelena: Kopiraj od leve proti desni.</para> </listitem> <listitem> "
"<para>Modra: Kopiraj od desne proti levi ali briši na desni strani v "
"asimetričnem načinu.</para> </listitem> <listitem> <para>Rdeča: Datoteke, ki "
"se razlikujejo glede na podana merila (brez smeri kopiranja).</para> </"
"listitem> <listitem> <para>Črna: Datoteke, ki so enake (brez smer kopiranja)."
"</para> </listitem> </itemizedlist> Dvojni klik na datoteko prikliče "
"&krusader;-jevo funkcijo <guilabel>Primerjava po vsebini</guilabel>. Stolpec "
"Opravila (&lt;=&gt;) določa privzeto smer kopiranja, ki jo lahko uporabnik "
"po potrebi spremeni. Okno z rezultati podpira vlečenje elementov v druga "
"okna ( povlecite [levo], &Shift;+povlecite [desno] ) in kopirajte levo/desno "
"izbrane elemente v odložišče (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</"
"keycap ></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>File List</guilabel>: Tasks (&lt;=&gt;) column"
msgstr "<guilabel>Seznam datotek</guilabel>: stolpec opravil (&lt;=&gt;)"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This column displays the task that is planned for the Synchronizer, this "
"task can be modified with the <link linkend=\"synccomp_right-click\">right "
"click menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta stolpec prikazuje nalogo, ki je načrtovana za sinhronizator, to nalogo je "
"mogoče spremeniti z <link linkend=\"synccomp_right-click\">menijem z desnim "
"klikom</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>-&gt;</guibutton>: Copy from the left side to the right side. For "
"folders: <command>mkdir</command> in the right side."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>-&gt;</guibutton>: Kopiraj z leve strani na desno. Za mape: "
"<command>mkdir</command> na desni strani."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>=</guibutton>: The files are the same, do not do anything."
msgstr "<guibutton>=</guibutton>: Datoteke so enake, ne storite ničesar."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>!=</guibutton>: The file is excluded, or the Synchronizer does "
"not know what to do."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>!=</guibutton>: datoteka je izključena ali pa sinhronizator ne "
"ve, kaj naj stori."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton>: copy from the right side to the left side. For "
"folders: <command>mkdir</command> in the left side"
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton>: kopiraj z desne na levo stran. Za mape: "
"<command>mkdir</command> na levi strani"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>DEL</guibutton>: delete files from the right side."
msgstr "<guibutton>DEL</guibutton>: izbriše datoteke z desne strani."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show options"
msgstr "Pokaži možnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can include/exclude particular file types. Those files, that are "
"not in the list, will be untouched at synchronization."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko vključite/izključite določene vrste datotek. Datoteke, ki jih ni "
"na seznamu, bodo pri sinhronizaciji nedotaknjene."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>-&gt;</guibutton>: Enable/Disable the copy task from left to "
"right."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>-&gt;</guibutton>: Omogoči/onemogoči opravilo kopiranja od leve "
"proti desni."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>=</guibutton>: Enable/Disable listing the equal files."
msgstr "<guibutton>=</guibutton>: Omogoči/onemogoči prikaz enakih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>!=</guibutton>: Enable/Disable listing the excluded / <quote>do "
"not know what to do</quote> files."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>!=</guibutton>: Omogoči/onemogoči prikazovanje izključenih / "
"<quote>ne vem, kaj storiti</quote> datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton>: Enable/Disable the copy task from right to "
"left."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&lt;-</guibutton>: Omogoči/onemogoči opravilo kopiranja od desne "
"proti levi."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Trash</guibutton>: Enable/Disable the file deleting from the left "
"side task."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Smetnjak</guibutton>: Omogoči/onemogoči brisanje datotek iz "
"opravila na levi strani."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Duplicates</guibutton>: Enable/Disable those files that exist on "
"both sides."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Dvojniki</guibutton>: Omogoči/onemogoči tiste datoteke, ki "
"obstajajo na obeh straneh."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Singles</guibutton>: Enable/Disable those files that exist only "
"on one side."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Posamezni</guibutton>: Omogoči/onemogoči tiste datoteke, ki "
"obstajajo samo na eni strani."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:440 synchronizer.docbook:679
#, no-c-format
msgid "Action buttons"
msgstr "Akcijski gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Compare</guibutton>: Compares the folders, the results are "
"displayed on the <guilabel>File List</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Primerjaj</guibutton>: Primerja mape, rezultati so prikazani na "
"<guilabel>Seznamu datotek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: Stops comparing."
msgstr "<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton>: Ustavi primerjavo."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Synchronize</guibutton>: Shows the synchronize dialog."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Sinhroniziraj</guibutton>: Prikaže pogovorno okno za "
"sinhronizacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: Closes the Synchronizer window."
msgstr "<guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>: Zapre okno sinhronizatorja."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:467
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Status line may contain"
msgstr "Statusna vrstica lahko vsebuje"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of scanned folders while comparing."
msgstr "Število pregledanih map med primerjavo."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid "The filename when comparing by content (for big files)."
msgstr "Ime datoteke pri primerjavi po vsebini (za velike datoteke)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of files on the list."
msgstr "Število datotek na seznamu."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right click menu on the <guilabel>File List</guilabel>"
msgstr "Desni klik na meni <guilabel>Seznam datotek</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "The right click menu is split up in three sections:"
msgstr "Meni z desnim klikom je razdeljen na tri dele:"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"1. change the <guilabel>Task</guilabel> operations determined by the "
"Comparator. Select one or multiple files. The change will be applied on the "
"selection and not only on the right clicked item. If the selected item is a "
"folder, the change will be applied on its files/subfolders as well."
msgstr ""
"1. spremenite operacije <guilabel>Opravila</guilabel>, ki jih določi "
"primerjalnik. Izberite eno ali več datotek. Sprememba bo uporabljena na "
"izboru in ne samo na elementu, ki ga kliknete z desnim klikom. Če je izbrani "
"element mapa, bo sprememba uporabljena tudi v njenih datotekah/podmapah."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Synchronize Folders...</guibutton>: Starts synchronization."
msgstr "<guibutton>Sinhroniziraj mape ...</guibutton>: Zažene sinhronizacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Exclude</guibutton>: Excludes a file/dir from synchronization "
"( task change to != )."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Izključi</guibutton>: Izključi datoteko/imenik iz sinhronizacije "
"(naloga se spremeni v !=)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Restore original operation</guibutton>: Task change to the "
"original result of comparison."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Obnovi prvotno operacijo</guibutton>: Sprememba opravila na "
"prvotni rezultat primerjave."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Reverse direction</guibutton>: Task change ( -&gt; to &lt;-, and "
"&lt;- to -&gt; )."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Obratna smer</guibutton>: Sprememba naloge (-&gt; v &lt;- in "
"&lt;- v -&gt;)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Copy from right to left</guibutton>: Task change to &lt;-."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Kopiraj od desne proti levi</guibutton>: Naloga se spremeni v "
"&lt;-."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Copy from left to right</guibutton>: Task change to -&gt;."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Kopiraj od leve proti desni</guibutton>: Naloga se spremeni v -"
"&gt;."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Delete ( left single )</guibutton>: Task change to DEL."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Izbriši ( levo enojni )</guibutton>: Naloga se spremeni v DEL."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "2. change the selections"
msgstr "2. spremenite izbire"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Select items</guibutton>: Opens a dialog which allows you to "
"select items. This is the <guimenuitem>Select Group</guimenuitem> dialog "
"from the <link linkend=\"edit-menu\">Edit menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Izberi elemente</guibutton>: odpre pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča "
"izbiro elementov. To je pogovorno okno <guimenuitem>Izberi skupino</"
"guimenuitem> v <link linkend=\"edit-menu\">meniju Uredi</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Unselect items</guibutton>: Opens a dialog which allows you to "
"deselect items. This is the <guimenuitem>Unselect Group</guimenuitem> dialog "
"from the <link linkend=\"edit-menu\">Edit menu</link>."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Prekliči izbor elementov</guibutton>: odpre pogovorno okno, ki "
"vam omogoča, da prekličete izbor elementov. To je pogovorno okno "
"<guimenuitem>Prekliči izbiro skupine</guimenuitem> v <link linkend=\"edit-"
"menu\">meniju Uredi</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Invert selection</guibutton>: Invert the selection status of all "
"items."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Obrni izbor</guibutton>: obrne status izbire vseh elementov."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"3. others (note that the following operations work on the right-clicked file "
"and not on the selection)."
msgstr ""
"3. drugi (upoštevajte, da naslednje operacije delujejo na datoteko, ki jo "
"kliknete z desno tipko miške, in ne na izbor)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>View left file</guibutton>: Starts viewer on the left file."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Ogled leve datoteke</guibutton>: Zažene pregledovalnik na levi "
"datoteki."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>View right file</guibutton>: Starts viewer on the right file."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Ogled desne datoteke</guibutton>: Zažene pregledovalnik na desni "
"datoteki."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Compare Files</guibutton>: Starts the diff utility (&eg; "
"&kompare;) on the files."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Primerjaj datoteke</guibutton>: Zažene pripomoček za razlikovanje "
"(&eg; &kompare;) v datotekah."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other buttons"
msgstr "Drugi gumbi"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Profiles</guibutton>: If you have to synchronize the same folders "
"often, you can save the settings &eg; include files, exclude files, ... "
"Press the <guibutton>Profile</guibutton> button, and you will be able to "
"add / load / save / remove synchronizer profiles."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Profili</guibutton>: Če morate pogosto sinhronizirati iste mape, "
"lahko shranite nastavitve &eg; vključi datoteke, izključi datoteke, ... "
"Pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Profil</guibutton> in lahko boste dodali / "
"naložili / shranili / odstranili profile sinhronizatorja."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Swap sides</guibutton>: Swaps the <guilabel>File List</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Zamenjaj strani</guibutton>: Zamenja <guilabel>Seznam datotek</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronize with <application>kget</application>"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj z <application>kget</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to synchronize a local folder with an unstable &FTP; server, "
"<application>kget</application> is a much better solution than simple file "
"copying. After comparing you may right click on the result list and select "
"<guimenuitem>Synchronize with KGet</guimenuitem> to execute the "
"synchronization, after that the listed files will be downloaded with "
"<application>kget</application> instead of &krusader;. Of course "
"<application>kget</application> needs to be installed on your computer; "
"otherwise, it will not be available."
msgstr ""
"Če želite sinhronizirati lokalno mapo z nestabilnim &FTP; strežnik, je "
"<application>kget</application> veliko boljša rešitev kot preprosto "
"kopiranje datotek. Po primerjavi lahko z desno miškino tipko kliknete na "
"seznam rezultatov in izberete <guimenuitem>Sinhroniziraj s KGet</"
"guimenuitem>, da izvedete sinhronizacijo, nato pa bodo navedene datoteke "
"prenesene z <application>kget</application> namesto z &krusader;. Seveda "
"mora biti <application>kget</application> nameščen na vašem računalniku; "
"sicer ne bo na voljo."

#. Tag: title
#: synchronizer.docbook:619
#, no-c-format
msgid "Synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After pressing the <guibutton>Synchronize</guibutton> button the "
"synchronization dialog appears."
msgstr ""
"Ko pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Sinhroniziraj</guibutton>, se prikaže "
"pogovorno okno za sinhronizacijo."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check boxes"
msgstr "Potrditvena polja"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you confirm the copy and delete operations of the Synchronizer"
msgstr "Tukaj potrdite operacije kopiranja in brisanja sinhronizatorja"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Right to left</guilabel>: copy X1 files ( Y1 bytes ) enable / "
"disable the copy from right to left."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Od desne proti levi</guilabel>: kopirajte datoteke X1 ( Y1 "
"bajtov ) omogočite/onemogočite kopiranje od desne proti levi."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Left to right</guilabel>: copy X2 files ( Y2 bytes ) enable / "
"disable the copy from left to right."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Od leve proti desni</guilabel>: kopirajte datoteke X2 ( Y2 "
"bajtov ) omogočite/onemogočite kopiranje od leve proti desni."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:644
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Left</guilabel>: delete X3 files ( Y3 bytes ) enable / disable the "
"left side deleting."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Levo</guilabel>: izbriši datoteke X3 ( Y3 bajtov ) omogoči/"
"onemogoči brisanje na levi strani."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Confirm overwrites</guilabel>: By switching this option on, "
"Krusader will show the <guibutton>rename, skip, overwrite, skip all, "
"overwrite all</guibutton> dialog box, before overwriting the file."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Potrdi prepise</guilabel>: Če vklopite to možnost, bo Krusader "
"pred prepisom datoteke prikazal pogovorno okno <guibutton>preimenuj, "
"preskoči, prepiši, preskoči vse, prepiši vse</guibutton>."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Status labels"
msgstr "Oznake stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Ready</guilabel>: A1/A2 files, B1/B2. This line is changed at "
"synchronizing, showing that synchronizer finished with A1 files from A2 ( B1 "
"bytes from B2 )."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pripravljeno</guilabel>: datoteke A1/A2, B1/B2. Ta vrstica se "
"spremeni pri sinhronizaciji, kar kaže, da je sinhronizator končal z "
"datotekami A1 iz A2 (bajti B1 iz B2)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Progress bar</guilabel>: Shows the progress on the synchronization "
"(based on bytes)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vrstica napredka</guilabel>: Prikazuje napredek pri sinhronizaciji "
"(na osnovi bajtov)."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Start</guibutton>: Starts synchronization."
msgstr "<guibutton>Zaženi</guibutton>: Zažene sinhronizacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Pause / Resume</guibutton>: Pauses/resumes the synchronization "
"process."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Premor / Nadaljuj</guibutton>: Začasno ustavi/nadaljuje proces "
"sinhronizacije."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton>: Closes the synchronization dialog (and stops "
"synchronization)."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Zapri</guibutton>: Zapre pogovorno okno za sinhronizacijo (in "
"ustavi sinhronizacijo)."

#. Tag: term
#: synchronizer.docbook:702
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parallel synchronization"
msgstr "Vzporedna sinhronizacija"

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:706
#, no-c-format
msgid "One can give the number of the 'quasi' threads."
msgstr "Lahko podamo število 'kvazi' niti."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:710
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Can drastically increase the speed when synchronized with slow &FTP; servers."
msgstr ""
"Lahko drastično poveča hitrost pri sinhronizaciji s počasnim &FTP; strežniki."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid "Does not affect the speed of local synchronization."
msgstr "Ne vpliva na hitrost lokalne sinhronizacije."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remote <quote>compare by content</quote> and <quote>folder compare</quote> "
"is done in parallel."
msgstr ""
"Oddaljena <quote>primerjava po vsebini</quote> in <quote>primerjava map</"
"quote> poteka vzporedno."

#. Tag: para
#: synchronizer.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remote synchronization is also done in parallel, except the <command>mkdir</"
"command> tasks (<command>mkdir</command> must be before copy)."
msgstr ""
"Oddaljena sinhronizacija se izvaja tudi vzporedno, razen opravil "
"<command>mkdir</command> (<command>mkdir</command> mora biti pred "
"kopiranjem)."
